                <p class="sm-mb-5 m-0">Hospice care is typically recommended when a physician determines a life expectancy of six months or less, should the illness follow its usual course. Other signs that hospice may be appropriate include:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-1 text-center text-lg-start" style="">
