                    <li>Difficulty breathing during normal activities or while at rest</li>
                    <li>Severe fatigue and weakness that limits daily activities</li>
                    <li>Inability to perform daily activities without experiencing symptoms</li>
                    <li>Recurrent hospitalizations or ER visits for heart failure symptoms7</li>
                    <li>Co-existing conditions such as diabetes, kidney disease, COPD, or recent stroke</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="m-0">If you’re unsure about eligibility, our team can coordinate with your cardiologist to assess your loved one’s needs.</p>
